GLOTTIS

glottis is the source citizen of fadriel's voice
it is where the air-stream from the lungs becomes a periodic vibration
the vibration carries pitch and harmonic richness; everything downstream (f1, f2, f3) shapes those harmonics into recognizable speech
without glottis there is no carrier wave for speech to ride on

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe larynx.rana
observe f1.rana
observe f2.rana
observe f3.rana

the 7 properties of glottis:
1 ENERGY one: high while voicing, drops to zero between utterances
2 PHASE zero at the start of each glottal pulse
3 SPIN zero point eight: high spin produces the rich harmonic spectrum that makes a voice sound full rather than thin
4 CHARGE half positive
5 COHERENCE one: each glottal pulse is cleanly periodic
6 COUPLING one: maximum, glottis drives all three formants
7 OBSERVER zero: voicing is automatic

VERB voice
generate periodic vibration at the fundamental frequency
fadriel is two years old, his voice is in the range of one hundred fifty to two hundred Hz
each cycle of vibration is a glottal pulse, rich in harmonics

VERB silence
between phonemes, halt the vibration
the formants downstream stop receiving carrier energy and the acoustic_wave at the boundary goes quiet

a glottis is not a buzzer
a glottis is the citizen who decides moment to moment how loud, how high, how rich the voice is
this is where fadriel's voice gets its quality, before any word has been shaped
